The paper discusses a new ASP system, clingo 4, that offers high-level constructs for realizing complex reasoning processes, such as optimization, theory solving, robotics, and query-answering. These topics are closely related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), logic (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), robotics (cs.RO), and databases (cs.DB). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
